5","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","label":"Yes","uuid":"91e2b443-2bce-49a5-a728-dcab3ef7cd5a","parentUuid":"72099c46-16e7-47a2-a320-cc768b7085fe","metricMeasures":[]},{"annotations":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","text":"There are several questions regarding the dynamics of the data in the working area, who works with it, the software that is run on it, etc.","entityUuid":"df36fb68-131c-4f31-a42b-684abf523bbc","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"How will you work with your data?","requiredPhaseUuid":"1796fa3c-9f53-475f-89ff-c66a0453c42e","tagUuids":[],"uuid":"8bf13cec-a764-4fd1-81da-78815a3bc6b7","parentUuid":"e7324e1a-bfcb-4f2b-855a-35701dfb1ad5"},{"advice":null,"annotations":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","entityUuid":"5af813b7-cb41-4eb9-afe7-ca364771b74e","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","label":"Explore","uuid":"016c0515-aed5-4f4f-a7dd-ebcd6e74063d","parentUuid":"df36fb68-131c-4f31-a42b-684abf523bbc","metricMeasures":[]},{"annotations":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","text":"When making the work space, it helps to know whether you expect to work with very many small files, a few very large files, whether you will use a (SQL) database to store most of the data. Maybe your data is suitable for a system like Hadoop? Such information can be collected here.","entityUuid":"73bfcfcf-a619-4f6a-a901-2e8ce01d039a","questionType":"ValueQuestion","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"What kind of data will you have in your work space?","requiredPhaseUuid":"1796fa3c-9f53-475f-89ff-c66a0453c42e","tagUuids":[],"uuid":"d64ed222-9d70-4396-b1c8-f4a245534ee5","parentUuid":"5af813b7-cb41-4eb9-afe7-ca364771b74e","valueType":"TextQuestionValueType"},{"annotations":[],"createdAt":"2018-10-01T00:00:00Z","text":"If you have large volumes of data that are intensely and repeatedly used by the computing work flow, it may be needed to keep the storage in the same place as where the computing takes place.","entityUuid":"f6e66f4f-7b11-420f-