 will be clearly numbered","uuid":"332e5e26-3046-4661-9464-bd488108af72","parentUuid":"05655914-e1f4-4578-a7d4-bae17579fce8","metricMeasures":[]},{"annotations":{"changed":false},"createdAt":"2020-11-11T10:49:19.845Z","text":{"value":"Imagine yourself trying to interpret a similar data set from a colleague in a few years. \nIs there any way in which the data could be misinterpreted? Does everyone in the field do things in exactly the same way? And will that still be known in 10 years?\nHow can such misinterpretation be avoided?","changed":true},"entityUuid":"44a9d6c0-f96c-47d2-8c7a-902a9c222067","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","eventType":"EditQuestionEvent","title":{"changed":false},"requiredPhaseUuid":{"changed":false},"tagUuids":{"changed":false},"uuid":"ea56edc6-ecca-4a13-99b5-50ac9d7fb7bf","expertUuids":{"changed":false},"parentUuid":"a23664b1-a17c-41fe-855c-db274984b355","answerUuids":{"changed":false},"referenceUuids":{"changed":false}},{"annotations":{"changed":false},"createdAt":"2020-11-11T10:49:19.845Z","text":{"changed":false},"entityUuid":"feb954c1-c38e-4615-addd-4c714a06809a","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","eventType":"EditQuestionEvent","title":{"value":"Has authority over the data been arranged for when the project is finished (potentially long after)?","changed":true},"requiredPhaseUuid":{"changed":false},"tagUuids":{"changed":false},"uuid":"075ae527-9963-40b7-835e-d9333abebc1b","expertUuids":{"changed":false},"parentUuid":"d748ea2b-bbe7-4b05-82e2-bee5e10e8441","answerUuids":{"changed":false},"referenceUuids":{"changed":false}},{"advice":{"changed":false},"annotations":{"changed":false},"createdAt":"2020-11-11T10:49:19.845Z","entityUuid":"f68a6141-3f78-4efb-8a80-2a482e75a862","eventType":"EditAnswerEvent","followUpUuids":{"changed":false},"label":{"value":"Through a Data Access Committee","changed":true},"uuid":"b0f03c0c-f053-4271-a927-93c758a5fd59","parentUuid":"f78fb7e9-2f26-493c-a19b-04e153c17274","metricMeasures":{"changed":false}},{"annotati